{"tid":2318538,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"方仲賢准保 嘆港人庭外奔波","createTime":"2020-12-09T11:43:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T00:05:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4cb845df05db9ecd2462d6ae857fabe0d4218901","tid":2318538,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T11:43:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201209/AOQCYXGXFZGL3H6EXY6CM5EUWE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201209%2FAOQCYXGXFZGL3H6EXY6CM5EUWE%2F&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUCfW%2F3rzywXjCQwsEwiLy3M%3D&h=3a3230ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201209%2FAOQCYXGXFZGL3H6EXY6CM5EUWE%2F&h=710a95b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201209/AOQCYXGXFZGL3H6EXY6CM5EUWE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n方仲賢准保 嘆港人庭外奔波<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bQOMTiKBQDGLLiDmUT33vR51scA=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MAPFXBPOYVAFDPNIRWTI2GGC34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbQOMTiKBQDGLLiDmUT33vR51scA%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMAPFXBPOYVAFDPNIRWTI2GGC34.jpg&h=df4117c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n方仲賢<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港浸會大學學生會署理會長方仲賢（圖）去年在深水埗因購買觀星筆被捕，事後獲釋，惟至上周三突遭警方上門拘控。案件昨提堂，將轉介區域法院審理。方獲准以一萬元保釋候訊，期間除了不得離港、晚上9時至翌早7時更要宵禁。方事後於庭外慨嘆，香港人去年在街頭狂奔，今年則在法庭外「狂奔」，若他最終被判囚，望家人及友人不要比自己難過。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n強調沒可能修補撕裂<br />\n<br />\n方仲賢坦言，最近思緒混亂，僅是12月初已有多人被捕，每天均會發生不公義的事，已成港人日常。他稱港府經常聲稱要修補撕裂，但他強調沒有可能，因多名政治人物與區議員已被捕或流亡，香港永遠不能變回以前的香港。他又透露在審訊過程中最辛苦的並非自己，而是朋友和家人，「如果我要被判監，希望（佢哋）唔好比我更加難過」，並呼籲大家繼續關注被送中12港人。<br />\n<br />\n方被控三罪，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n方於案發後曾表示，案發當日在深水埗購買觀星筆後，遭多名便衣警員截停和襲擊，他更數度被箍頸，遭逼至牆角。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKCC4261/20"},{"pid":"8a93da73ae5e32b545691d128f4de50e1c4ebfb1","tid":2318538,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T00:05:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}